OL,3,CJust 7% confident justice system can
OL,4,Cdeliver for crime victims
OL,6,FJust 7% of victims of crime are fairly
OL,7,Fconfident that Northern Ireland's
OL,8,Fcriminal justice system can deliver
OL,9,Ffor them, a survey has found.
OL,11,FIn addition, 63% contend police did
OL,12,Fnot investigate their case properly
OL,13,Fand 50% were dissatisfied with how
OL,14,Fthey were treated by the Public
OL,15,FProsecution Service (PPS).
OL,17,FCommissioner-designate for Victims of
OL,18,FCrime Geraldine Hanna described the
OL,19,Ffindings of the research published on
OL,20,FMonday as an "SOS message from
OL,21,Fvictims".
