OL,3,CJust 7% confident justice system can
OL,4,Cdeliver for crime victims
OL,6,FThe 2023/24 survey, described as the
OL,7,Ffirst in the region to seek the view
OL,8,Fof victims of all crimes, also found
OL,9,Fjust 9% believe they got enough
OL,10,Fsupport during the court process.
OL,12,FWhile 7% feel fairly confident the
OL,13,Fjustice system can deliver for
OL,14,Fvictims, none said they are very
OL,15,Fconfident it can do so.
OL,17,FOne of the victims who responded to
OL,18,Fthe survey described their experience
OL,19,Fas "so damaging", adding: "I felt like
OL,20,Fa small fish in a tank full of sharks
OL,21,Fwho were always circling.
