OL,3,CJust 7% confident justice system can
OL,4,Cdeliver for crime victims
OL,6,F"I would not want anyone else to be
OL,7,Ftreated the way I was."
OL,9,FThe survey was carried out online
OL,10,Fbetween September 2023 and March 2024
OL,11,Fand is set to act as a baseline to
OL,12,Fmeasure the experience of victims of
OL,13,Fcrime in future.
OL,15,FMs Hanna said: "These results are
OL,16,Fnothing short of an SOS from victims
OL,17,Fof crime. Sadly this is not surprising
OL,18,Fand reinforces what we have heard from
OL,19,Fvictims before.
