OL,3,CJust 7% confident justice system can
OL,4,Cdeliver for crime victims
OL,6,F"This has to be a wake-up call to
OL,7,Fevery part of our system.
OL,9,F"From our elected leaders, through to
OL,10,Fthe criminal justice agencies, we need
OL,11,Fa fundamental change on how victims of
OL,12,Fcrime are treated here.
OL,14,F"There is no doubt in my mind that the
OL,15,Ffailure in the care and support of
OL,16,Fvictims has contributed to the poor
OL,17,Fconfidence levels that victims have in
OL,18,Fthe system and its ability to deliver
OL,19,Fjustice."
