OL,6,FThe PSNI victims' champion, Assistant
OL,7,FChief Constable Ryan Henderson, said:
OL,8,F"As a victim-focused service our
OL,9,Fofficers and staff have worked
OL,10,Ftirelessly to keep people safe and
OL,11,Ftackle the issues that matter to the
OL,12,Fcommunities we serve, against a
OL,13,Fbackdrop of increasingly limited
OL,14,Fresources and growing demand."
