OL,6,FHowever, Mr Henderson said he most
OL,7,Frecent policing plan survey
OL,8,Fcommissioned by the Northern Ireland
OL,9,FPolicing Board found that 91% of those
OL,10,Fwho took part would feel confident
OL,11,Fcontacting the PSNI and that 70% were
OL,12,Fsatisfied in the work they do.
OL,14,FHe added: "We have a close working
OL,15,Frelationship and I look forward to
OL,16,Fcontinue working with the commissioner
OL,17,Fdesignate to understand in more detail
OL,18,Fthe issues outlined in the survey."
