OL,6,FThe Public Prosecution Service's
OL,7,Fsenior assistant director and victims
OL,8,Fchampion, Marianne O'Kane, said the
OL,9,Fservice is under significant
OL,10,Fresourcing pressure but added that
OL,11,Fconviction rates remain high.
OL,13,FShe said: "The PPS faces similar and
OL,14,Finterlinked challenges to every
OL,15,Fcriminal justice agency. As well as
OL,16,Fadequate funding, a strategic
OL,17,Fgovernment approach is needed to
OL,18,Ftackle some of its most deep-rooted
OL,19,Fissues including delay in the system.
